@startuml
!include ../common/theme.puml
title 新增客戶：元件/模組架構（Component）

package "Frontend (Vite + Vue3 + ElementPlus)" {
  [Dashboard.vue] as Dashboard
  [useLongSpeechInput] as LongSpeech
  [parseCustomerCreate] as Parser
  [useAiSpeech] as AiSpeech
  [socket.js] as SocketUtil
  [customer_create.vue (iframe)] as CustomerCreate
  [MultiInputCard] as MultiInput
}

package "Backend" {
  [Flask API\n/api/form/customer_create/save] as ApiSave
  [Options API\n/api/form/customer_create/options] as ApiOptions
  [Socket Server\n(ai_command / ai_response)] as SocketSrv
}

Dashboard --> LongSpeech : stopAndCommit()\n(長語音)
Dashboard --> Parser : 本地解析\n新增客戶指令
Dashboard --> CustomerCreate : postMessage PREFILL\n(同源 iframe)
CustomerCreate --> MultiInput : v-model arrays\naddresses/tel/etc.
CustomerCreate --> ApiSave : save payload
CustomerCreate --> ApiOptions : loadOptionsByKey
Dashboard --> SocketUtil : connect/init events
SocketUtil --> SocketSrv : ai_command/ai_response
Dashboard --> AiSpeech : 語音指令導航\n(非新增客戶時)

note right of CustomerCreate
  Prefill 走 postMessage
  儲存成功回傳 CUSTOMER_CREATE_SAVED
end note

@enduml
